OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,FResident doctors in England will
OL,7,Fstrike for the 16th time in their long-
OL,8,Frunning dispute with the government
OL,9,Fover pay.
OL,11,FAnnouncing the four-day walkout from
OL,12,FJune 15 to 19, the British Medical
OL,13,FAssociation (BMA) said new Health
OL,14,FSecretary James Murray had not
OL,15,Fimproved the government's proposal,
OL,16,Fand there was still the "same
OL,17,Funwillingness to move" they
OL,18,Fexperienced with his predecessor Wes
OL,19,FStreeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
