FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,FDr Jack Fletcher, chair of the
OL,7,Fresident doctors committee, said: "We
OL,8,Fwere prepared to give Mr Murray time
OL,9,Fto settle into his role before
OL,10,Fcompleting the work his predecessor
OL,11,Fleft unfinished ` to both make a fair
OL,12,Fand meaningful pay offer and make
OL,13,Fconcrete commitments to end the jobs
OL,14,Fbottleneck throttling the careers of
OL,15,Four colleagues.
OL,17,F"He had a genuine opportunity to break
OL,18,Fthis logjam with fresh energy and
OL,19,Fambition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,F"Instead, we are hearing the same
OL,7,Ftired line: vagueness on new jobs and
OL,8,Fno further money on the table.
OL,10,F"Thousands of doctors continue to
OL,11,Fleave the NHS, and take-home pay
OL,12,Fremains a fifth lower in real terms
OL,13,Fthan it was in 2008.
OL,15,F"If Mr Murray wishes to make a success
OL,16,Fof his new role, he must confront this
OL,17,Fissue before any other. We are
OL,18,Fprepared to accept that he may have
OL,19,Finherited plans already in motion when
OL,20,Fhe took office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,F"Our ask is straightforward: a
OL,7,Fcredible, meaningful offer comprising
OL,8,Fconcrete new jobs and real progress
OL,9,Ftowards pay restoration."
OL,11,FThe June strike will be the 16th to
OL,12,Ftake place in England since 2023.
OL,14,FThe health secretary had met with
OL,15,Frepresentatives from the BMA earlier
OL,16,Fon Wednesday in hopes of finding an
OL,17,Fagreement with resident doctors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,FMurray had said he wanted to "give
OL,7,Funions confidence" and would do all he
OL,8,Fcan to improve career prospects and
OL,9,Fensure NHS staff are paid fairly.
OL,11,FResident doctor members last went on
OL,12,Fstrike in April for six days over the
OL,13,FEaster Holidays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,FAt the time, the government had
OL,7,Fproposed a 4.9% increase in average
OL,8,Fbasic pay from 2026 to 2027, with
OL,9,FStreeting stating this reflected a
OL,10,F32.5% pay rise compared with four
OL,11,Fyears ago, and was "the limits of what
OL,12,Fis affordable, deliverable and fair to
OL,13,Fpatients and taxpayers".
OL,15,FThe proposal had also included an
OL,16,Foffer of 1,000 extra training places,
OL,17,Fbut this was taken off the table the
OL,18,Fweek before the strike was due to
OL,19,Fbegin, as the Department of Health
OL,20,Fsaid it was no longer "financially or
OL,21,Foperationally" possible.
OL,26,@|D@WOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
