OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779898263
OL,3,CResident doctors announce 16th strike
OL,4,Cin dispute over pay
OL,6,FDr Fletcher accused the government of
OL,7,F"quietly watering down" the deal for
OL,8,Fresident doctors at the 11th hour, and
OL,9,Fthe strike went ahead.
OL,11,FStreeting initially struck a deal to
OL,12,Fend strikes by resident doctors during
OL,13,Fthe first months of the Labour
OL,14,Fgovernment in 2024, but action resumed
OL,15,Fin 2025.
OL,17,FThe cumulative cost of the walkouts is
OL,18,Festimated to have topped #3 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
